FBIS4-45588 "jptdd028__l94088" JPRS-TDD-94-028-L JPRS Narcotics 27 June 1994 WEST EUROPE FRANCE Police Launch `Huge' Operation Against Colombian Drug Cartels Police Launch `Huge' Operation Against Colombian Drug Cartels LD2706081994 Paris France-Inter Radio Network in French 0700 GMT 27 Jun 94 LD2706081994 Paris France-Inter Radio Network French BFN [Text] There has been a huge police operation in Paris, Marseille, Montpellier, and Limoges this morning, reportedly aimed at the interests in France of Colombian drug cartels, their cocaine distribution and money-laundering networks. Apparently it is a very large scale operation, and the end of many years' worth of investigation.
